*''The Family'' (1906)
*''Religious Chastity''
*''The Old-Fashioned Woman'' (1913)
*''Fear and Conventionality'' (1914)
*''Social Freedom'' (1915)
*''Social Rule'' (1916)

===人类学著作===
*''The Social Organization of the Tewa of New Mexico'' (1929)
*''Hopi and Zuni Ceremonialism'' (1933)
*''[http://books.google.com/books?id=vf10J97nm1QC Pueblo Indian Religion] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=vf10J97nm1QC |date=20121111055732 }}'' (1939)

